<p>The <a href="/wiki/Glottal_stop" title="Glottal stop">glottal stop</a> &lt;ъ&gt; is often omitted when writing.</p>
<p>In 1992, a new Latin Chechen alphabet was introduced, but after the defeat of the secessionist government, the Cyrillic alphabet was restored.</p>
