<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b> <span class="citation book">Amjad M. Jaimoukha (2005). <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=O56A3HB4jo4C&amp;pg=PA239&amp;dq=preserve+their+language+and+culture+chechens+syria+iraq&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=xorLTeyyFM64twfWuszbBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CDEQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=preserve%20their%20language%20and%20culture%20chechens%20syria%20iraq&amp;f=false" class="external text" rel="nofollow"><i>The Chechens: a handbook</i></a>. Psychology Press. p.&#160;239. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0415323282" title="Special:BookSources/0415323282">0415323282</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=O56A3HB4jo4C&amp;pg=PA239&amp;dq=preserve+their+language+and+culture+chechens+syria+iraq&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=xorLTeyyFM64twfWuszbBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CDEQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=preserve%20their%20language%20and%20culture%20chechens%20syria%20iraq&amp;f=false" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=O56A3HB4jo4C&amp;pg=PA239&amp;dq=preserve+their+language+and+culture+chechens+syria+iraq&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=xorLTeyyFM64twfWuszbBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CDEQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=preserve%20their%20language%20and%20culture%20chechens%20syria%20iraq&amp;f=false</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved May 12 2011</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Chechens%3A+a+handbook&amp;rft.aulast=Amjad+M.+Jaimoukha&amp;rft.au=Amjad+M.+Jaimoukha&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B239&amp;rft.pub=Psychology+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0415323282&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DO56A3HB4jo4C%26pg%3DPA23